        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer778934371" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12580874129876856085">I loved the backstory of Alexander Graham Bell as it coincided with the current day story, it has given me the desire to read more about Bell&apos;s personal life. My favorite quotes &quot;What is false about hope?&quot; and Faith is believing without the need for proof. I would read this story again. </span>
  <span id="freeText12580874129876856085" style="display:none">I loved the backstory of Alexander Graham Bell as it coincided with the current day story, it has given me the desire to read more about Bell's personal life. My favorite quotes "What is false about hope?" and Faith is believing without the need for proof. I would read this story again. </span>
