<span id="freeTextContainer12841462340914476460">It&apos;s such an enjoyable and an inspiring read from Mitch Albom! He never fails to make me emotional. I recommend this book to everyone.<br/><br/>I love how this book focuses on different characters. Each one of them experienced of losing someone they love or someone closest to their hearts. Their faith has been tested, believing that God exists and there is life after death. Also coping up with loss. Miracles indeed happen in life, but miracles will come if you pray to God for guidance and of course, you h</span>
  <span id="freeText12841462340914476460" style="display:none">It's such an enjoyable and an inspiring read from Mitch Albom! He never fails to make me emotional. I recommend this book to everyone.<br /><br />I love how this book focuses on different characters. Each one of them experienced of losing someone they love or someone closest to their hearts. Their faith has been tested, believing that God exists and there is life after death. Also coping up with loss. Miracles indeed happen in life, but miracles will come if you pray to God for guidance and of course, you have to work for it. <br /><br />Praises to Mitch Albom! </span>
